      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "For the most part, these cars were sheep in wolves' clothing. It's not GM's fault though, really – the one-two punch of a fuel crisis and new federal emissions standards really knocked the wind out of a lot of performance cars. The Camaro Z28 was no exception."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "However, someone decided that enough was enough – they were going to do something about it. They were going to give the late second-gen Z28 the performance it deserved."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      10,
      2
    ],
